詳情






     Fenix 自九歲習琴, 於香港浸會大學取得學士學位(音樂)後, 後獲全額獎學金及研究生助學金赴美國貝勒大學取深造, 師承Krassimira Jordan及Vincent De Vries, 以鋼琴獨奏及鋼琴合奏雙碩士學位畢業, 並於2008年獲Roger L. Keyes傑出研究生獎。
   其後赴奧地利維也納音樂大學, 隨Thomas Kreuzberger及Barbara Moser習琴, 並取得鋼琴獨奏及室樂合奏深造文憑。在留美期間曾擔任學系之鋼琴伴奏, 現活躍於鋼琴演奏及伴奏, 不時擔任音樂比賽評判,曾於漢基國際學校任鋼琴導師。在2016年8月, Fenix被邀請參加在MuTh- 維也納兒童合唱團音樂廳舉行之貝多芬鋼琴奏鳴曲馬拉松.


 
學歷:
維也納國立音樂大學, 研究文憑 (鋼琴,室樂)
貝勒大學, 音樂碩士(鋼琴演奏)
貝勒大學, 音樂碩士(鋼琴伴奏)
香港浸會大學音樂系, 榮譽學士(鋼琴演奏)
 
資歷:
英國皇家音樂學院高級演奏文憑
英國皇家音樂學院八級樂理 

 
 
 
 
     Fenix Man has been studying the piano since the age of 9. After graduated from the Hong Kong Baptist University, he furthered his study in the Baylor University (USA) with full scholarship and postgraduate assistantship. He gained his Dual Master Degree in piano performance and collaborative piano under the tutelage of Ms Krassimira Joradn and Dr. Vincent de Vries. In addition, he received the Roger L. Keyes Award for outstanding graduate student in piano in 2008.
 
 
 
      Fenix then further studied with Thomas Kreuzberger and Barbara Moser in the University for Music and Performing Arts Vienna and attained a postgraduate diploma in piano performance and chamber music. During his stay in the US, Fenix has been the piano accompanist for the School of Music in Baylor University. He is now an active performer and a sought-after accompanist, as well as competition judge. He taught in Chinese International School. In 2016 summer, Fenix was invited to perform for the Beethoven piano sonata marathon in MuTh - Concert Hall of the Vienna Boys Choir, Vienna. 

 
Education and Academic Qualifications:
Postgraduate diploma,Klavier, Lied und Kammermusik, Universität für Musik und darstellende Kunst Wien
Master of Music, Collaborative piano major, Baylor University
Master of Music, Piano performance major, Baylor University
Bachelor of Arts (Hons) in Music, performance major, Hong Kong Baptist University
 
 
 
 
 
Further Qualifications:
 
Advanced Certificate (Piano), The Associated Board of the Royal Schools of Music
Grade 8 (Theory), The Associated Board of the Royal Schools of Music
 
 

 

超過10年教學/伴奏經驗,
根據多年留美,歐洲之經驗,
引用音樂學院之全面培訓特式,
加強技巧和音樂感的均衡發展.

另外,
在鋼琴課上,
強調aural,sight reading的訓練,
每堂都加入一定之訓練
可確保學生在考試經常失落的aural , sightreading部份,
取得佳績.
 
 
現正招收1-8級, 演奏級之鋼琴學生
